 1       | server2  | 5432 | up     | up        | 0.333333  | replica | replica | 0          | false             | 0                 |                   |                        | 2021-12-02 16:48:21
 2       | server3  | 5432 | up     | up        | 0.333333  | replica | replica | 0          | false             | 0                 |                   |                        | 2021-12-02 16:48:21
(3 rows)
